      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Rein Halbersma</b>\n</p><p><b>Rein Halbersma</b>,<br />\na Dutch <a href=\"/Draughts\" title=\"Draughts\">Draughts</a> and <a href=\"/Checkers\" title=\"Checkers\">Checkers</a> programmer, and author of the <i>Draughts and Checkers Template Library DCTL</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. He is further interested in computer chess and chess programming, and active poster in <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Computer Chess Forums</a>.  \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2007_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2007 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n