ste.info/bb3/index.php\">World Draughts Forum</a>, March 05, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50388\">How could a compiler break the lockless hashing method?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rein Halbersma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 08, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Shared_Hash_Table\" title=\"Shared Hash Table\">Shared Hash Table</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rein_Halbersma&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58647\">Unifying make/undo and copy-make</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rein Halbersma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 21, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Copy-Make\" title=\"Copy-Make\">Copy-Make</a>, <a href=\"/Unmake_Move\" title=\"Unmake Move\">Unmake Move</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=66929\">LCZero update (2)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rein Halbersma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 25, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Leela_Chess_Zero\" title=\"Leela Chess Zero\">Leela Chess Zero</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=70584&amp;start=5\">Re: Wouldn't it be nice if C++ GPU</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rein Halbersma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 25, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a>, <a href=\"/GPU\" title=\"GPU\">GPU</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span 